task.question: Find two different meanings of the word "harmony" in the Cambridge Dictionary.
task.answer: Meaning 1: a pleasant musical sound made by different notes being played or sung at the same time; Meaning 2: a situation in which people are peaceful and agree with each other, or when things seem right or suitable together
